data.description: *Ask about the 'assumable mortgage' on this property. If you are already approved for an FHA or VA loan, you can save thousands when compared to today's interest rates!* Welcome to the Green Ridge community featuring this 2022 NEW CONSTRUCTION that is ready to move into NOW! No need to wait!!! This open-concept build exemplifies the convenience of main-level living. The gorgeous all-white kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a large island with seating and a friendly dining area welcome you and your loved ones for all your parties and events! The large and stylish living room is ready for your hosting delights! The updated and stylish recess lighting shines bright in the evening and the big windows allow for plenty of fresh, natural daylight during the day! The home features a large and luxurious primary bedroom with an en suite, a full private bath, and a spacious walk-in closet that would be the envy of your friends! Two more nice bedrooms are offered in this home along with a 2nd full bathroom. A bright 2-car attached garage welcomes you home showing off its space and storage capability. Finally, the full, tall, and bright basement is ready for your vast vision and ideas on how to best use this blank canvas of space. Green Ridge is about 15 minutes from Dekalb and has easy access to Rt 30 and Rt 23. It is less than 10 minutes from Shabbona State Park known for its wonderful campgrounds, boating, fishing, and hiking. This home really is a dream and can be yours today! Welcome HOME!
